- Never edit files under collaboration/state/** or CI configs.
- Follow branch naming: feat/<task-id>-slug.
- Only use MCP tools: context.get, search.repo/query, tests.run/execute. 
- MCP calls must respect lane permissions (Implementer: context.get + search.repo/query; Planner: search.repo/query + context.get; Critic: tests.run/execute + search.repo/query + context.*).
- Commit style: conventional commits (feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore, ci, build, revert).
- Definition of Done: updated tests, typecheck/lint clean, docs updated, critic approval.
- Use Context Reset Protocol: reset context between tasks, rehydrate only task ID, acceptance, CHANGESCOPE.
